1. Create a counter contract for increment and decrement. Emit event for both. 
• Increment by 5
• decrement by 2
• set default value 4

2. Create a contract that takes input string from the user and sets new value, restrict this so that only 
   owner of the contract can do this 

3. Create a mapping that maps bookId to author name. Add three methods to 
• add the values
• get the values
• delete the mapping

4. Create a dynamic sized array for country names. Add three methods to 
• add the country names
• delete the countries from the array
• return the array size

5. Create a structure named “School” for “studentName” and “rollNo”. Add two methods to 
• add new student to the structure
• get the studentName by rollNo.
• Get the rollNo by studentName
